@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kadzla(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.29)) / wp.sin((v2 + 0.02 * v1 + 0.85)))
    v1 = (tmp - ((v1 + 0.02 - v1 + 0.07) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.81)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.76)))
    data[tid] = v0
